item.title: Top 5 Machine Learning Code Repositories from Singapore
item.description: tl;dr We feature 5 of the top machine learning code repositories on Github from Singapore. The ranking is decided based on the total stars (stargazer count) of the repositories. 5. PyTorch Implementation of EfficientDet Architecture of EfficientDet including a weighted bi-directional feature pyramid network (BiFPN). A PyTorch implementation of the 2019 Computer Vision paper EfficientDet: Scalable and Efficient Object Detection from Google Brain. The official implementation by Google Brain is in TensorFlow.
